\v 26 \x + \xo 4:26: \xt 1Ki 17:8-16.\x*\wj But Eliyah wasn't sent to any of themвҖ”rather he was sent to a \+add foreign\+add* widowВҰ40957 in Zarephath in the Tsidon regionВҰ40953.\wj*
\v 27 \x + \xo 4:27: \xt 2Ki 5:1-14.\x*\wj Also there were many people in Yisrael with leprosy in the days of the prophetВҰ40968 ElishaВҰ40966 andВҰ40972 none of them were healed, but only NaamanВҰ40978 from SyriaВҰ40980.\wj*вҖқ
