\p
\v 22 ThenВҰ50628 Yeshua told his followers, вҖң\wj That's why I'm telling you all not to worryВҰ50639 about your lifestyle: what to eatВҰ50644 or what to wear,\wj*
\v 23 \wj becauseВҰ50652 your lifeВҰ50653 is more than food and your bodyВҰ50660 is more than clothingВҰ50662.\wj*
\v 24 \wj Look at the ravensВҰ50670. They don'tВҰ50673 plant seeds or harvest crops and they have no storeroomsВҰ50682 or barns, yet \+nd GodВҰ50689\+nd* keeps them fed, and \+add humans\+add* are worth a lot more than birdsВҰ50699.\wj*
\v 25 \wj Which of youВҰ50703 can add even an hourВҰ50712 to yourВҰ50702 life by spending more time worryingВҰ50704?\wj*
\v 26 \wj SoВҰ50715 if you can'tВҰ50716 even do something small like that, why worryВҰ50728 aboutВҰ50724 bigger things?\wj*
\v 27 \x + \xo 12:27: \xt 1Ki 10:4-7; 2Ch 9:3-6.\x*\wj Look at how the liliesВҰ50731 grow. They don'tВҰ50745 go to work or make \+add fabric\+add*, yet even \+add King\+add* SolomonВҰ50746 at the height of hisВҰ50751 fame wasn't dressed as well as one of them.\wj*
\v 28 \wj So if \+nd GodВҰ50781\+nd* dressesВҰ50783 the weeds in the paddock that are here todayВҰ50774 and incinerated tomorrowВҰ50776, how much more would he look after you allвҖ”you with littleВҰ50788 faithВҰ50788?\wj*
\p
\v 29 вҖң\wj So don't all be lookingВҰ50792 forВҰ50792 what to eatВҰ50794 or to drinkВҰ50799, andВҰ50803 don't \+add waste time\+add* by worrying\wj*
\v 30 \wj becauseВҰ50808 people in every country in the worldВҰ50813 are lookingВҰ50816 forВҰ50816 that, but yourВҰ50817 fatherВҰ50822 \+add already\+add* knows that you need those things.\wj*
\v 31 \wj Rather youВҰ50840 should be striving \+add to enter\+add* hisВҰ50833 kingdomВҰ50832, andВҰ50836 then all theseВҰ50837 things will come as a bonus.\wj*
