\p
\v 32 вҖң\wj Don't be afraid, littleВҰ50844 flockВҰ50845, becauseВҰ50846 \+add actually\+add* yourВҰ50853 fatherВҰ50852 takes pleasureВҰ50849 in giving you the entireВҰ50853 kingdomВҰ50857.\wj*
\v 33 \wj Sell what you own and giveВҰ50863 to the poor \+add and so\+add* store yourВҰ50861 wealth in heavenВҰ50874 whereВҰ50875 it won'tВҰ50868 deteriorate or get lost or stolen \+add from you\+add*,\wj*
\v 34 \wj becauseВҰ50884 where your wealth is stored, that's where your mindВҰ50893 will be \+add focused\+add*.\wj*
\s1 The well-prepared slave
