\v 41 ThenВҰ51036 PeterВҰ51039 asked, вҖң\nd MasterВҰ51040\nd*, is that parableВҰ51045 just for us, or is it for everyone?вҖқ
\p
\v 42 The master answered, вҖң\wj SoВҰ51052 what would a faithfulВҰ51062 andВҰ51052 wise slave be like, thatВҰ51081 the master might make into a managerВҰ51064 over all hisВҰ51080 slaves, the one to give them their rationsВҰ51089?\wj*
