\v 45 \wj In contrast, if that slave thought to himself that the masterВҰ51131 might be away for a long time, he might start beating the slave boysВҰ51139 and slave girlsВҰ51142, and start ordering feasts, and drinkingВҰ51148 and getting drunkВҰ51151,\wj*
\v 46 \wj then hisВҰ51177 master is sure to arrive when he's not expectingВҰ51164 him, and the master will give him a gruesome execution and he'll be \+add in hell\+add* with the unbelieversВҰ51181.\wj*
