\v 47 вҖң\wj Any slaveВҰ51186 who knows what their masterВҰ51192 wants, yet doesn't get anything ready or start doing what's wanted, they'll get a good beating,\wj*
\v 48 \wj yet a slave that didn'tВҰ51209 know what was expected, even if they might have done things worthyВҰ51213 of a beatingВҰ51214, they'll just get a couple of blowsВҰ51216. Everyone who's givenВҰ51221 much is expected to do much, andВҰ51219 everyoneВҰ51218 who's entrustedВҰ51236 with many things, will have much more expected \+add back\+add* from them.\wj*
