\v 49 вҖң\wj I cameВҰ51245 to throwВҰ51246 fire onto the earthВҰ51250, andВҰ51251 how I wish that itВҰ51256 was alreadyВҰ51255 kindledВҰ51256,\wj*
\v 50 \x + \xo 12:50: \xt Mrk 10:38.\x*\wj butВҰ51258 I have to undergo an immersionВҰ51257 \+add into suffering\+add*, andВҰ51261 untilВҰ51264 it's achieved, the weight of it \+add coming\+add* crushes my \+add soul\+add*.\wj*
\v 51 \wj You all \+add probably\+add* expect that I came to bring peace to the earthВҰ51280. No, I'm telling you, \+add not peace\+add* but conflict,\wj*
\v 52 \wj becauseВҰ51291 from now on, if there's five \+add people\+add* in one houseВҰ51299, they'll be split with three against two and two against three.\wj*
\v 53 \x + \xo 12:53: \xt Mic 7:6.\x*\wj Fathers will be in conflict with their sons, and sons with fathers, mothers against daughters and daughters against mothers, mothers-in-law against their daughters-in-law and daughters-in-law against mothers-in-law.\wj*вҖқ
