\v 14 \x + \xo 13:14: \xt Exo 20:9-10; Deu 5:13-14.\x*But the hall leaderВҰ51779 was angry because it was the Rest Day when \nd Yeshua\nd* had healed her and started telling the crowdВҰ51789, вҖңThere's six daysВҰ51796 when it's fine to work, so come then to be healedвҖ”not on the Rest Day!вҖқ
