\v 15 вҖң\wj \+add You\+add* hypocrites!\wj*вҖқ Yeshua respondedВҰ51824. вҖң\wj Doesn't every one of you untie hisВҰ51837 ox on the Rest Day, or untie the donkeyВҰ51842 from the feeding trough andВҰ51817 lead it away for a drinkВҰ51850?\wj*
\v 16 \wj This woman is a descendant of AbrahamВҰ51855 who's been handicapped by SatanВҰ51861 for eighteenВҰ51866 yearsВҰ51867, andВҰ51865 \+add yet you say\+add* that it's wrong to break that bond on the Rest Day!\wj*вҖқ
\v 17 When he said thatВҰ51903, the people opposingВҰ51888 him were disgracedВҰ51884 andВҰ51880 all the crowdВҰ51893 was excited about the wonderful things he was doing.
