\p
\v 18 SoВҰ51911 he told them, вҖң\wj What is God's kingdomВҰ51917 similarВҰ51914 to? What can I use to describe it?\wj*
\v 19 \wj It's like a mustardВҰ51927 seed, whichВҰ51928 a person might take and throwВҰ51932 into their gardenВҰ51935 and then it grows in a bush and the birdsВҰ51947 make their nests in itsВҰ51959 branchesВҰ51957.\wj*вҖқ
