\v 20 Again he asked them, вҖң\wj What can I likenВҰ51965 God's kingdomВҰ51970 to?\wj*
\v 21 \wj It's like some yeast thatВҰ51981 a womanВҰ51983 took and hid in a sack of flourВҰ51987, untilВҰ51992 \+add eventually\+add* it affected all of it.\wj*вҖқ
