\v 24 \wj becauseВҰ54984 when humanity's child returns, it'll be like lightningВҰ54986 that flashesВҰ54988 from one side of the sky and shines right across to the other side.\wj*
\v 25 \wj However, before that, he needs to sufferВҰ55017 many things andВҰ55019 to be rejectedВҰ55020 by this generationВҰ55023.\wj*
\v 26 \x + \xo 17:26: \xt Gen 6:5-8.\x*\wj The time of \+add the return of\+add* humanity's child will be just like it was in Noah's time:\wj*
\v 27 \x + \xo 17:27: \xt Gen 7:6-24.\x*\wj people were eatingВҰ55043 and drinkingВҰ55044, and getting engaged and married right untilВҰ55048 that dayВҰ55050 when NoahВҰ55052 wentВҰ55051 into the barge and the floodВҰ55060 came and destroyedВҰ55063 everything.\wj*
