\v 29 \wj but on the dayВҰ55083 that LotВҰ55085 walked out of SodomВҰ55087, fireВҰ55089 and sulfur rainedВҰ55088 down from the skyВҰ55095 and destroyedВҰ55097 everything.\wj*
