\p
\v 31 \x + \xo 17:31: \xt Mrk 13:15-16; Mat 24:17-18.\x*вҖң\wj On that dayВҰ55121, anyone who's just outside the house shouldВҰ55137 not go back in to get their valuables. Similarly, anyone who's out on the farm shouldn'tВҰ55136 returnВҰ55147 to the house to get \+add their possessions\+add*.\wj*
