\v 33 \x + \xo 17:33: \xt Yhn 12:25; Mrk 8:35; Mat 10:39; 16:25; Luk 9:24.\x*\wj Anyone who tries to save their live will lose it, and anyone who's \+add sacrificed\+add* their lifestyle, will retain lifeВҰ55164.\wj*
\v 34 \wj I'm telling youВҰ55182, twoВҰ55189 \+add people\+add* will be in one bed on that nightВҰ55186 and one will be takenВҰ55196 and the otherВҰ55200 one will be left \+add behind\+add*.\wj*
\v 35 \wj Two \+add people\+add* will be preparing food at the sameВҰ55212 placeВҰ55212 and one will be takenВҰ55215 and the otherВҰ55219 one will be left \+add behind\+add*.\wj*вҖқ
\p
\v 36 в—ҳ
