\v 3 \wj Now there was a widowВҰ55286 in that cityВҰ55291, andВҰ55293 sheВҰ55294 \+add kept\+add* going to himВҰ55296 sayingВҰ55297, вҖҳ\+add вүҲGet me justice\+add* against myВҰ55303 rival.вҖҷ\wj*
\v 4 \wj \+add вүҲAt first\+add*, he wasn't \+add вүҲinterested in the case\+add*, but \+add вүҲeventually\+add* he saidВҰ55316 to himselfВҰ55319, вҖҳEven if I don'tВҰ55305 fear \+nd GodВҰ55326\+nd* andВҰ55304 \+add вүҲI'm not easily pushed around by anyone\+add*,\wj*
\v 5 \wj this widowВҰ55343 is \+add вүҲmaking\+add* troubleВҰ55340 for me. I'll \+add вүҲfight her case for her so she'll stop\+add* harassingВҰ55353 me.вҖҷ\wj* вҖқ
