\v 8 \wj I'm telling you that he'll quicklyВҰ55404 bring \+add вүҲjustice\+add* \+add to the situation\+add*. HoweverВҰ55405, when humanity's child comes, will he find faithВҰ55415 on the earthВҰ55418?\wj*вҖқ
