\v 19 вҖң\wj Why do you call me good?\wj*вҖқ \nd Yeshua\nd* respondedВҰ55642. вҖң\wj No one is good other than \+nd GodВҰ55658\+nd* himself.\wj*
\v 20 \x + \xo 18:20: a \xt Exo 20:14; Deu 5:18; \xo b \xt Exo 20:13; Deu 5:17; \xo c \xt Exo 20:15; Deu 5:19; \xo d \xt Exo 20:16; Deu 5:20; \xo e \xt Exo 20:12; Deu 5:16.\x*\wj You know \+add &God's\+add* commandsВҰ55660: Don't commitВҰ55673 adulteryВҰ55673, don't murderВҰ55677, don't stealВҰ55681, don't lie in court, andВҰ55691 honourВҰ55687 yourВҰ55690 parents.\wj*вҖқ
