\p
\v 28 PeterВҰ55819 spoke up, вҖңHey, \em weВҰ55821\em* left everything andВҰ55825 followedВҰ55829 youВҰ55830!вҖқ
\p
\v 29 вҖң\wj I can assure youВҰ55837 all,\wj*вҖқ Yeshua respondedВҰ55833, вҖң\wj that no one who left their home or spouse or siblings, or parentsВҰ55855 or childrenВҰ55857 on accountВҰ55862 of God's kingdomВҰ55864\wj*
