\v 32 \wj He'll be handed over to non-Jews and will be mockedВҰ55922 and insultedВҰ55924 and spat on,\wj*
\v 33 \wj thenВҰ55927 they'll flog him andВҰ55927 kill him, but he'll come back to life on the thirdВҰ55935 dayВҰ55933.\wj*вҖқ
