\v 40 ThenВҰ56030 \nd Yeshua\nd* stoppedВҰ56029 andВҰ56030 orderedВҰ56033 that the man be broughtВҰ56035 \add across\add* to him. When he came, he askedВҰ56041 him,
\v 41 вҖң\wj What do you want me to do for you?\wj*вҖқ
