\p
\v 28 After he'd saidВҰ56634 that, Yeshua continuedВҰ56634 on towards Yerushalem,
\v 29 and as he got near to BethfageВҰ56647 and BethanyВҰ56649 going towardsВҰ56650 the MtВҰ56652. of OlivesВҰ56657, he sentВҰ56659 twoВҰ56660 of his followers ahead,
\v 30 telling \add them\add*, вҖң\wj Go on to the next villageВҰ56670, and when you enterВҰ56674 it, you'll see a colt that's never been ridden tied up there. Untie it and bringВҰ56687 it \+add here\+add*.\wj*
\v 31 \wj ButВҰ56689 if anyoneВҰ56692 asks you why you're untyingВҰ56697 it, tell them that the \+nd masterВҰ56703\+nd* needs it.\wj*вҖқ
