\v 36 ThenВҰ56767 as the colt moved along, theyВҰ56769 spreadВҰ56769 \add more of\add* their clothesВҰ56771 on the roadВҰ56776.
\p
\v 37 As he was about to descend down the slope of the MountВҰ56789 of OlivesВҰ56791, the whole crowdВҰ56798 of followers started celebrating andВҰ56779 loudlyВҰ56806 praisingВҰ56802 \nd GodВҰ56804\nd* for all the miraclesВҰ56813 they'd seen,
\v 38 \x + \xo 19:38: \xt Psa 118:26.\x*sayingВҰ56814, вҖңThe comingВҰ56817 kingВҰ56819 has been blessedВҰ56815 in the nameВҰ56821 of \nd YahwehВҰ56822\nd*. \add May there be\add* peaceВҰ56831 in heavenВҰ56828 andВҰ56833 brilliant splendour up high there.вҖқ
\p
\v 39 There were some members of the Pharisee partyВҰ56842 in the crowdВҰ56846 andВҰ56837 they suggested to himВҰ56849, вҖңTeacherВҰ56850, tell yourВҰ56854 followers to stop!вҖқ
\p
\v 40 вҖң\wj I'm telling youВҰ56862,\wj*вҖқ Yeshua answeredВҰ56856, вҖң\wj that if all of theseВҰ56865 people stayed silentВҰ56868 thenВҰ56855 the stonesВҰ56870 would start shouting.\wj*вҖқ
