\v 43 \wj because in the future, yourВҰ56922 enemiesВҰ56921 will surroundВҰ56926 you and build a palisadeВҰ56923 aroundВҰ56919 you and attack you from everyВҰ56932 side.\wj*
\v 44 \wj Then they'll levelВҰ56934 you and yourВҰ56939 childrenВҰ56938 along with you, and they'll topple the stone \+add walls and buildings\+add*, because you didn'tВҰ56943 realise \+add the importance of\+add* who was visitingВҰ56962 you.\wj*вҖқ
