\v 5 They discussed this among themselvesВҰ57148, reasoningВҰ57144, вҖңIf we sayВҰ57152 вҖҳfrom heavenВҰ57154вҖҷ, thenВҰ57143 he'll ask us why we didn'tВҰ57160 believeВҰ57161 \add that God sent himВҰ57162\add*.
\v 6 But if we say вҖҳfrom peopleвҖҷ, then all the people will kill us with rocks, becauseВҰ57183 they believe that Yohan was a prophetВҰ57187.вҖқ
