\v 21 They askedВҰ57493 himВҰ57494, вҖңTeacherВҰ57497, we know that you say what is right, andВҰ57492 that you teach the truthВҰ57512 about God's wayВҰ57514 without \add being influenced\add* by people.
\v 22 \add So tell us,\add* should we pay taxВҰ57522 to the \add Roman\add* emperor or not?вҖқ
\p
\v 23 But havingВҰ57529 observedВҰ57529 theirВҰ57531 craftinessВҰ57534, he saidВҰ57535 to them,
