\v 37 \x + \xo 20:37: \xt Exo 3:6.\x*\wj But about the dead beingВҰ57792 raisedВҰ57792, Mosheh revealed it at the \+add burning\+add* thornВҰ57801 bush when he called \+nd YahwehВҰ57804\+nd* the god of AbrahamВҰ57807 and of IsaacВҰ57811 and of YacobВҰ57815,\wj*
