\rem /s1 Warnings about the end; The Widow's Offering
\r (Mark 12:41-44)
\p
\v 1 When Yeshua lookedВҰ57961 up, he sawВҰ57963 some wealthyВҰ57976 people throwingВҰ57965 theirВҰ57974 giftsВҰ57973 into the \add temple\add* treasuryВҰ57971 \add basket\add*.
\v 2 He \add also\add* noticed a poor widowВҰ57982 who threw in twoВҰ57988 small copper coins.
