\p
\v 8 вҖң\wj Be careful,\wj*вҖқ he answered, вҖң\wj in case you all get deceived, becauseВҰ58101 lots of people will come using myВҰ58106 nameВҰ58105 andВҰ58095 sayingВҰ58107, вҖҳI'm him,вҖҷ or вҖҳThe timeВҰ58113 has come.вҖҷ Don't follow afterВҰ58118 them,\wj*
\v 9 \wj and wheneverВҰ58120 you all hearВҰ58122 about wars and disturbancesВҰ58125, don't be terrifiedВҰ58128, becauseВҰ58130 all theseВҰ58131 things do need to happen firstВҰ58134, but they don't mean that the endВҰ58139 will be right thenВҰ58121.\wj*вҖқ
\p
\v 10 Then heВҰ58141 told them, вҖң\wj Various countries andВҰ58148 kingdoms will attack each other\wj*
