\p
\v 12 вҖң\wj But before all that happens, they'll be arresting you all, and persecutingВҰ58189 you. You'll be handed over to the meetingВҰ58193 hallsВҰ58193 and prisonsВҰ58195. \+add Some of you\+add* will be stood in front of kingsВҰ58199 and governorsВҰ58201 because of myВҰ58205 nameВҰ58204\wj*
