\v 14 \x + \xo 21:14-15: \xt Luk 12:11-12.\x*\wj SoВҰ58213 be confident that you all don'tВҰ58221 need to figure out in advance what you will say in yourВҰ58220 defenceВҰ58224\wj*
\v 15 \wj becauseВҰ58226 I'll give you the words to say and wisdomВҰ58232 whichВҰ58233 all of those opposingВҰ58245 you won'tВҰ58234 be able to resistВҰ58239 or speakВҰ58241 againstВҰ58241.\wj*
\v 16 \wj But you'll also be turned in even by parentsВҰ58251 and siblings, \+add other\+add* relativesВҰ58255 and friendsВҰ58257, and some of you will be \+add sentenced\+add* to deathВҰ58261.\wj*
