\v 20 вҖң\wj However, when you all seeВҰ58293 Yerushalem beingВҰ58294 surroundedВҰ58294 by armiesВҰ58297, then you'll knowВҰ58301 that \+add the time of\+add* herВҰ58309 abandonment is close.\wj*
\v 21 \wj Then those who are in YudeaВҰ58314 should flee to the hills and those in the central area should get out, and foreigners should no longer go there\wj*
\v 22 \x + \xo 21:22: \xt Hos 9:7.\x*\wj because thatВҰ58340 will be a time of vengeanceВҰ58337 when what's been writtenВҰ58345 will come to pass.\wj*
\v 23 \wj It'll be so hard for pregnant and breast-feeding women at that time becauseВҰ58361 there'll be incredible distress in the country and severeВҰ58372 angerВҰ58372 towards the \+add Jewish\+add* peopleВҰ58375.\wj*
\v 24 \wj They'll be cut down with swordsВҰ58382 andВҰ58377 taken to many other countriesВҰ58389 as slaves, thenВҰ58377 Yerushalem will be overrun by non-Jews untilВҰ58397 the timesВҰ58402 \+add given to\+add* the non-Jews will be fulfilledВҰ58399.\wj*
