\p
\v 25 \x + \xo 21:25: \xt Isa 13:10; Eze 32:7; Yoel 2:31; Rev 6:12-13.\x*вҖң\wj There'll be signsВҰ58407 in the sunВҰ58409, the moonВҰ58411, and the starsВҰ58413, and anguishВҰ58418 in countriesВҰ58419 around the world as they're puzzled by the noise of the seaВҰ58427 and surf.\wj*
\v 26 \wj People will faintВҰ58431 from fearВҰ58434 and worry about what's happening to the planet, becauseВҰ58443 the powers in the universe\f + \fr 21:26 \ft This could possibly be referring to a shake-up of spiritual powers, but more likely refers to the physical universe from our moon and solar system outwards.\f* will be shakenВҰ58451.\wj*
\v 27 \x + \xo 21:27: \xt Dan 7:13; Rev 1:7.\x*\wj ThenВҰ58458 they'll see humanity's child comingВҰ58459 \+add down\+add* in a cloudВҰ58461 with powerВҰ58465 andВҰ58468 greatВҰ58471 brightness.\wj*
\v 28 \wj But when theseВҰ58475 things start to happen, stand straightВҰ58478 andВҰ58479 look upwards, becauseВҰ58484 yourВҰ58483 new lives of freedom will be about to beginВҰ58473.\wj*вҖқ
