\p
\v 29 ThenВҰ58489 he told them a parableВҰ58491: вҖң\wj WatchВҰ58493 the figВҰ58495 treeВҰ58495 andВҰ58489 all the treesВҰ58499.\wj*
\v 30 \wj Whenever you see shoots start appearing, you know that summerВҰ58521 is not far away.\wj*
