\p
\v 32 вҖң\wj I can assure youВҰ58542 all that that generationВҰ58548 certainly won'tВҰ58545 passВҰ58546 away untilВҰ58550 all those events \+add come to an end\+add*.\wj*
\v 33 \wj The sky andВҰ58558 the earthВҰ58560 will pass away, butВҰ58564 myВҰ58566 statements will certainly not pass away.\wj*
\s1 Stay alert and pray
