\p
\v 34 \wj Watch yourВҰ58582 own lives in case you end up focused on partying and drunkennessВҰ58586 and day-to-day livingВҰ58589, because thenВҰ58573 that suddenВҰ58595 end might snap on you\wj*
\v 35 \wj like an animal trap, becauseВҰ58603 itВҰ58602 will hit everyone all over the planet.\wj*
\v 36 \wj No matter what the seasonВҰ58620, stay alert, asking \+add God\+add* thatВҰ58630 you'll all have the strength to escapeВҰ58626 all those things goingВҰ58631 to happen, and \+add at the end to be able\+add* to stand in front of humanity's child.\wj*вҖқ
\p
\v 37 \x + \xo 21:37: \xt Luk 19:47.\x*ThenВҰ58642 Yeshua was teachingВҰ58649 in the templeВҰ58648 during the day, butВҰ58651 he'd leave in the evening and go and stay on the Mount of OlivesВҰ58662,
