\v 1 \x + \xo 22:1: \xt Exo 12:1-27.\x*By thenВҰ58681 the \it Flat Bread Celebration\it* was getting closerвҖ”part of the Passover celebrations,
\v 2 and the chiefВҰ58693 priestsВҰ58693 and the religiousВҰ58696 teachersВҰ58696 were trying to find a wayВҰ58698 to killВҰ58701 Yeshua \add without causing the peopleВҰ58707 to riot\add*.
